<section class="page">
<p class="first" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 80px;"><a href="/pages/contact" title="Contact Us" style="text-decoration: underline;">Contact us</a> to order a Mini Melanie signature cake.<br /><br />Choose from the sizes and flavors below. All cakes come with Mini Melanie signature drip and truffles on top. An inscription on your cake is always free!<br /><br />We require a minimum of two days notice. We accept rush orders for next day or same day delivery with an additional fee, based on the order. Each cake is made fresh to order for local New York City delivery (7 days a week) or pick-up, by appointment only, (Sunday through Friday).<br /><br />Our buttercream-covered cakes should be eaten at room temperature–so please store them in the fridge but remove them 2-3 hours before serving to allow the buttercream to become soft and creamy.</p>
